---
web3forms: true
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block head %}
  <title>Free SEO Audit | Find What's Broken | Freeland</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Get a free SEO audit for your website. We'll analyze your rankings, technical issues, and competitors — then show you exactly what to fix. Delivered in 48 hours." />
  <meta name="author" content="Kevin Freeland" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://freelandme.com/seo-audit/" />

  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://freelandme.com/seo-audit/" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Free SEO Audit | Find What's Broken | Freeland" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Get a free SEO audit for your website. We'll analyze your rankings, technical issues, and competitors — then show you exactly what to fix. Delivered in 48 hours." />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://freelandme.com/blog/images/service-seo-florida.jpg" />
  <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200" />
  <meta property="og:image:height" content="624" />
  <meta property="og:image:alt" content="Free SEO Audit — Find What's Broken on Your Website" />
  <meta property="og:image:type" content="image/jpeg" />
  <meta property="og:locale" content="en_US" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="Freeland Marketing &amp; Entertainment" />

  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Free SEO Audit | Find What's Broken | Freeland" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Get a free SEO audit for your website. We'll analyze your rankings, technical issues, and competitors — then show you exactly what to fix." />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://freelandme.com/blog/images/service-seo-florida.jpg" />
  <meta name="twitter:image:alt" content="Free SEO Audit — Find What's Broken on Your Website" />

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://freelandme.com/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Free SEO Audit", "item": "https://freelandme.com/seo-audit/" }
    ]
  }
  </script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

  <article>

    <header class="post-header">
      <div class="post-header-inner">
        <a href="/services/seo/" class="post-breadcrumb">&larr; Back to SEO Services</a>
        <span class="blog-category">Free Audit</span>
        <h1>Find Out What's Broken on Your Website</h1>
        <p style="color:#ccc;margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:1.05rem;">Enter your URL. We'll send you a detailed SEO report within 48 hours — completely free.</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-body">

      <form class="contact-form" action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" id="audit-form">
        <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="af9a5ef5-c8be-450b-8fdd-9039551baa76" />
        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Free SEO Audit Request" />
        <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="https://freelandme.com/thank-you.html" />
        <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="John Smith" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="john@yourbusiness.com" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="website">Website URL *</label>
            <input type="url" id="website" name="website" placeholder="https://yourbusiness.com" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(386) 555-0100" autocomplete="tel" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary btn-large btn-full">Get My Free SEO Audit &rarr;</button>
        <p class="form-note">100% free. No obligation. Report delivered within 48 hours.</p>
      </form>

      <h2>What You'll Get</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Site health score</strong> — broken links, missing tags, speed issues, and overall technical health of your website</li>
        <li><strong>Google presence check</strong> — how many pages are indexed, your Search Console status, and whether Google can actually find your content</li>
        <li><strong>Competitor snapshot</strong> — who's outranking you and why, with specific examples from your market</li>
        <li><strong>Critical issues list</strong> — the exact problems hurting your rankings right now, prioritized by impact</li>
        <li><strong>Action plan</strong> — exactly what to fix first for maximum impact on your search visibility</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="post-callout">
        <p><strong>Why It's Free</strong></p>
        <p>We believe business owners deserve to know the truth about their website. Most don't realize they have problems until someone shows them. That's what this audit does — no strings attached.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How long does the audit take?</summary>
          <p>We deliver your full SEO audit report within 48 hours of receiving your submission. Most audits are completed the same business day.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What do you actually check?</summary>
          <p>We review your technical SEO (speed, mobile, crawlability), on-page SEO (titles, descriptions, headings, content), current search rankings, competitor landscape, and Google Business Profile status. It is a comprehensive look at everything affecting your visibility on Google.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Is this really free?</summary>
          <p>Yes — 100% free. No credit card required, no hidden fees, no commitment. We provide the audit because it helps business owners understand where they stand. If you want help fixing what we find, we are here. If not, the report is still yours to keep.</p>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="post-cta-box">
        <h3>Ready to See What's Holding Your Site Back?</h3>
        <p>Enter your URL above and we will show you exactly what needs to be fixed — free, no strings attached.</p>
        <a href="#audit-form" class="btn-primary btn-large">Get My Free SEO Audit &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </article>

{% endblock %}
